{"tid":875044,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"超傻眼的神級組合！　橋本有菜與三上悠亞終於合體共演","createTime":"2018-10-24T15:45:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T13:49:13.000Z","uid":62257,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"191ea2dc3d9c65d7bcb8e2e508f9a48361a2b0b0","tid":875044,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:45:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=446512\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D446512&d=LocyWrPuCwFUSFEj7z139Z7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=ea6ae271\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D446512&h=e6e784dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=446512</a><br />\n<br />\n亞洲粉絲們所稱「神級組合」 終於要推出，上周末才剛領軍「Honey Popcorn」來台，舉辦完首度海外演唱會的日本成人女神三上悠亞，居然即將與合體今年甫出閣DMM成人獎2018年影后，偶像級女神橋本有菜，消息一出粉絲們馬上對強大的組合狂留言，直喊：「跪求我婆番號！」<br />\n<br />\n三上悠亞與橋本有菜兩人都有著超高顏質，2017年三上悠亞獲得DMM 成人影片頒獎典禮《最佳女優賞》，隔年2018年與松田美子、櫻萌子組成正規女子團體「Honey Popcorn」攻韓出專輯造成轟動，而今年2018 同樣DMM成人中獎獲得《最佳女優賞》的橋本有菜，正巧也與君色華奈、桐谷茉莉...等人宣布成立偶像團體「un panopticon girl」，本月3日在「MILKY POP GENERATION」推出CD出道。<br />\n<br />\n今年橋本有菜得獎時，正是由三上悠亞頒獎給她，現在「最強美腿」之稱的橋本有菜，搭配上超人氣成人偶像三上悠亞，兩人絕對是目前數一數二女神，根據日本S1官方近日公布，S1慶祝15周年推出「最強偶像與至高美少女」，由前、後兩屆女神在下個月合體推出作品，將與男優來場「三人共演」VR片。"},{"pid":"04d9862e8e8c1f780b18819a5d310c8799673e8e","tid":875044,"uid":35406,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:48:37.000Z","msg":"淨係想睇橋本"},{"pid":"0d4df33bf45dcb9ae40be0cc3c929b1a9148fff7","tid":875044,"uid":62257,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"04d9862e8e8c1f780b18819a5d310c8799673e8e","tid":875044,"uid":35406,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:48:37.000Z","msg":"淨係想睇橋本"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:56:52.000Z","msg":"咁隨時都有啦"},{"pid":"7ec48ea2d12ac8f3c1af28559c21e40760361d59","tid":875044,"uid":62257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:06:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb9cd157e21cb6450c9295ffc6ee169ab9aa360","tid":875044,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"04d9862e8e8c1f780b18819a5d310c8799673e8e","tid":875044,"uid":35406,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T15:48:37.000Z","msg":"淨係想睇橋本"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:44:24.000Z","msg":"+1"},{"pid":"9d4ce1621adcc897fca5248f9ce3d27d719953ab","tid":875044,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T16:50:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"387efbb16c6f531737b2f7b7baef4e7c901371e4","tid":875044,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T13:49:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}